Games also make their way into
daily life through gamification.

00:07:42.900 --> 00:07:46.920
This grows out of achievement systems some
video games use to reward players in

00:07:46.920 --> 00:07:51.040
addition to the normal game objectives.
These systems have proven to be very motivational,

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:54.280
